INDI ServoBlaster Cap 0.1 - (beta)
==================================

You must have CMake >= 2.8 in order to build this package.

indi_servoblaster_cap
==================

1) $ cd ~/Projects
2) $ git clone https://github.com/magnue/indi_servoblaster_cap.git
3) $ cd indi_servoblaster_cap
4) $ mkdir build
5) $ cd build
6) $ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr . ..
7) $ sudo make install

Dependencies
============

+ libindi and it's dependencies
    # To to build libindi from source 
        # http://www.indilib.org/forum/general/210-howto-building-latest-libindi-ekos.html

+ servoblaster
    $ cd ~/Projects
    $ git clone https://github.com/richardghirst/PiBits.git
    $ cd PiBits/ServoBlaster/user/
    $ sudo make servod
    $ ./servod

+ (optinal) INDI USBRelay2 Roof
    # To build from source
        # https://github.com/magnue/indi_usbrelay2_roof.git

+ (optional) WiringPi GPIO
    # To build from source
        # https://github.com/magnue/indi_wiringpi_gpio.git
